<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="purpose-n">purpose <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'pɜːpəs/    美 /'pɜːrpəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>目标；目的</strong></h4>
<p>the intention or aim of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What’s the <strong>purpose of</strong> your visit to London?
你去伦敦的目的是什么？</p><footer>外研⑥ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>For the purpose of</strong> helping protect Grand Canyon, please follow the guidelines below.
为了有助于保护大峡谷，请遵守如下准则。</p><footer>2008 四川</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Work gives you meaning and purpose and life is empty without it.
工作给了你意义和目标。没有工作的人生是空虚的。</p><footer>—— 霍金</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>用途；作用</strong></h4>
<p>the function of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tears <strong>serve no purpose</strong>.
眼泪无济于事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I haven’t got a pen, but a pencil can <strong>serve / answer the same purpose</strong>.
我没带钢笔，不过用铅笔也一样。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>用意；需要</strong></h4>
<p>what is needed in a particular situation：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Using animals <strong>for medical purposes</strong> should be avoided.
应避免用动物做医学实验。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>意义：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Volunteer work gives her life a <strong>sense of purpose</strong>.
志愿者工作让她的生活有了意义。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-purpose">on purpose</h3>
<p>1.<strong>故意地；有意地 (deliberately)</strong><br />
反 by accident： </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cinderella left her shoe on the stairs on purpose.
灰姑娘故意把自己的鞋落在楼梯上。</p><footer> 2014 福建</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>purposeful /'pɜːpəsfl/ adj <br />
purposely /'pɜːpəsli/ adv   </p></div>